import React from 'react'
import { Button, Typography, List, ListItem, ListItemButton } from '@mui/material'
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles'
import {
  SearchOutlined, LocationOnOutlined, LocalPostOfficeOutlined, ShoppingBagOutlined,
  PersonOutlineOutlined, FavoriteBorderOutlined
} from '@mui/icons-material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'



const MediumHeader = ({ title }) => {

  const MyStyledButton = styled(Button)(({ theme }) => ({
    fontFamily: 'Arial',
    textTransform: 'lowercase',
    padding: theme.spacing(2)
  }));

  return (
    <Box>
      <List>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemButton>
            <SearchOutlined />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemButton>
            <LocationOnOutlined />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
      </List>

      <Typography variant='h2' component="h1">{title}</Typography>

      <List>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemButton>
            <LocalPostOfficeOutlined />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemButton>
            <FavoriteBorderOutlined />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemButton>
            <PersonOutlineOutlined />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemButton>
            <ShoppingBagOutlined />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
      </List>
    </Box>
  )
}
 {/* <ButtonGroup>
        <Button variant='contained' color='myCustomColor' onClick={()=>{console.log("Hola Lola")}}>search</Button>
        <Button variant='contained' sx={{color:'myCustomColor.main'}} onClick={()=>{console.log("Hola Emma")}}>location</Button>
        <MyStyledButton variant='contained' color='secondary'>else</MyStyledButton>
        <Button variant='contained' sx={{width:"200px"}} >Fourth</Button>
      </ButtonGroup> */}
export default MediumHeader
